message: AO73/FUNcube-1 launched six years ago on Nov 21st 2013.  >32000 orbits & still going strong!
Hi - Season's greetings to all FUNcubers!
To request  a FITTER message, please email operations@funcube.org.uk
Congrats on reaching orbit to HuskySat-1. We look forward to some cross band link ups
FUNcube-1 is in full sunlight until Apr/May 2020
